OL,4,CCovid: Bus and train firms must decide
OL,5,Cwhether to require masks
OL,6, The government has said bus and train
OL,7, companies must decide whether
OL,8, passengers will be required to wear
OL,9, face coverings on their services from
OL,10, Monday, when Covid rules are relaxed.
OL,12,FFace masks have been mandatory on
OL,13,Fpublic transport for the past year to
OL,14,Freduce the spread of the virus.
OL,16,FBut those rules will be replaced with
OL,17,Fgovernment guidance advising passengers
OL,18,Fto wear masks only on busy services.
OL,20,FTransport firms will be left to decide
OL,21,Fwhether to enforce that advice and how.
